<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Welcome to 3Musafir</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .password-section {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 2px dashed #ff6b35;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .password-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .password-box {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 2px solid #ff6b35;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ff6b35;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        user-select: all;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .password-box:hover {
        background-color: #fff5f2;
        transform: scale(1.02);
      }
      .copy-hint {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-style: italic;
      }
      .info-box {
        background-color: #fff8e1;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffa726;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .info-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #666;
      }
      .message {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 25px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .signature {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }
      .signature p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #666;
      }
      .team-name {
        color: #ff6b35;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 25px 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }
        .password-box {
          font-size: 20px;
          padding: 12px 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>üéâ Welcome to 3Musafir!</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p class='greeting'>Dear Musafir,</p>

        <p class='message'>
          Thank you for your interest in joining the 3Musafir community. We're
          excited to have you on board and can't wait to start this journey with
          you!
        </p>

        <div class='password-section'>
          <div class='password-label'>Your Temporary Password</div>
          <div class='password-box'>{{password}}</div>
          <div class='copy-hint'>üëÜ Copy from above</div>
        </div>

        <div class='info-box'>
          <p>
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong>
            Please use this temporary password to log in and verify your email
            address as soon as possible to complete your account setup.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class='message'>
          We appreciate your support and look forward to exploring new horizons
          with you! If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to
          reach out to us.
        </p>

        <div class='signature'>
          <p>Best regards,</p>
          <p class='team-name'>The 3Musafir Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>
          This email was sent to you because you registered for a 3Musafir
          account.
        </p>
        <p style='font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 10px;'>
          ¬© 2025 3Musafir. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
